*uuidtools-2.1.3 (20 Jul 2012)

  20 Jul 2012; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +uuidtools-2.1.3.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  10 Jul 2012; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  +files/uuidtools-2.1.2-macaddress.patch, uuidtools-2.1.2.ebuild:
  Add patch to fix tests when network information is restricted (bug #425430).

  08 Mar 2011; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -uuidtools-1.0.7.ebuild,
  -uuidtools-2.1.1-r2.ebuild:
  Remove old versions.

  08 Mar 2011; Thomas Kahle <tomka@gentoo.org> uuidtools-2.1.1-r1.ebuild:
  x86 stable per bug 333867

  28 Feb 2011; Markos Chandras <hwoarang@gentoo.org> uuidtools-2.1.1-r1.ebuild:
  Stable on amd64 wrt bug #333867

